	<ol class="kntt-list" type="a"><li>$\heva{&\left(SAD\right) \cap \left(ABCD\right) = AD\\
		&\left(SAD\right) \bot \left(ABCD\right)\\
		& SM \subset \left(SAD\right), SM \bot AD
		}$ $\Rightarrow SM \bot \left(SAD\right)$\\
		$\Rightarrow \mathrm{d} \left(S;\left(ABCD\right)\right) = SM$.</li><li>Gọi $N$ là trung điểm $AO$ $\Rightarrow MN \bot AO$.\\
		Kẻ $MP \bot SN$\\
		Ta có $\heva{&AO \bot MN\\&AO \bot SM}$ $\Rightarrow AO \bot \left(SMN\right)$\\
		$\Rightarrow AO \bot MP$ mà $MP \bot SN$\\
		$\Rightarrow MP\bot \left(SAC\right) \Rightarrow \mathrm{d}\left(M;\left(SAC\right)\right) = MP$.\\
		Ta có $\dfrac{\mathrm{d}\left(M;\left(SAC\right)\right)}{\mathrm{d}\left(D;\left(SAC\right)\right)} = \dfrac{1}{2} \Rightarrow \mathrm{d}\left(D;\left(SAC\right)\right) = 2 MP$.</li><li>Vì $\heva{&AB \bot AD \\& AB \bot SM } \Rightarrow AB \bot \left(SAD\right) \Rightarrow AB = a = \mathrm{d}\left(B;\left(SAD\right)\right)$.</li><li>Kẻ $AT \bot SD$.\\
		Vì $\heva{&AT \bot SD\\&AT\bot AB \left(do  AB \bot \left(SAD\right)  và  AT \subset \left(SAD\right) \right)}$\\
		$\Rightarrow SD = \mathrm{d}\left(SD;AB\right)=\dfrac{a\sqrt{3}}{2}$</li></ol>

